subfilterRules.help:
A regular expression matched against key names. Only values whose key
matches are processed by the subfilter. Used together with `subfilter`;
when omitted, the subfilter applies to all extracted values.

includeStyles.help:
When non-empty, only text in one of the listed styles is extracted;
all other text is skipped. Leave it empty (the default) to apply no
style-based restriction.

variant.help:
Selects the markup dialect to parse: `dokuwiki` or `mediawiki`. The
default is `dokuwiki` to match the upstream `okf_wiki` bridge contract;
choose `mediawiki` for MediaWiki-flavoured markup.
